SpiceSynth includes repository-local code as well as functionality built on top
of `spice-opl3-nuked` and `spice-adl-adplug`. The project is now distributed
under LGPL-2.1-or-later as a single licensing model to simplify packaging and
dynamic-link distribution guidance.
